nodes.text: The  fusial thrust engine was a type of engine used on X-wing starfighter models. Incom Corporation's T-65B X-wing featured 4L4 fusial thrust engines or 4j.4 fusial thrust engines, and the Incom-FreiTek Corporation T-70 X-wing featured 5L5 fusial thrust engines. The T-85 X-wings also had fusial thrust engines.
